.TP
.B $<OUTPUT_CONFIG:...>
Added in version 3.20.

.sp
Only valid in \fBadd_custom_command()\fP \%<#\:command:add_custom_command> and \fBadd_custom_target()\fP \%<#\:command:add_custom_target>
as the outer\-most generator expression in an argument.
With the \fBNinja Multi\-Config\fP \%<#\:generator:Ninja Multi-Config> generator, generator expressions
in \fB\&...\fP are evaluated using the custom command\(aqs \(dqoutput config\(dq.
With other generators, the content of \fB\&...\fP is evaluated normally.
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B $<COMMAND_CONFIG:...>
Added in version 3.20.

.sp
