the \fB<CONFIG>_POSTFIX\fP \%<#\:prop_tgt:<CONFIG>_POSTFIX> and \fBDEBUG_POSTFIX\fP \%<#\:prop_tgt:DEBUG_POSTFIX> target
properties.
.sp
Note that \fBtgt\fP is not added as a dependency of the target this
expression is evaluated on.
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
