\fB<CONFIG>_POSTFIX\fP \%<#\:prop_tgt:<CONFIG>_POSTFIX> target properties, is always included in the
\fBPDB\fP base name, except if the \fBPOSTFIX\fP option has the value
\fBEXCLUDE\fP\&.  See the policy \fBCMP0202\fP \%<#\:policy:CMP0202>\&.

